\layout Standard


\begin_inset Formula \[
\nu_{v}=\nu_{12}-v\,\nu_{1}\quad\Rightarrow v=\frac{\nu_{12}-\nu_{v}}{\nu_{1}}\]

\end_inset 

La probabilidad de emisión (
\begin_inset Formula $e',v\rightarrow e,0$
\end_inset 

