\begin_inset Formula \[
A_{e'e}\left(\nu_{v}\right)=A_{e'e}\, F_{0,\left(\nu_{12}-\nu_{v}\right)/\nu_{1}}=A_{e'e}\, g(\nu_{e},\nu_{v})\]

